sequenceDiagram
    participant Config
    participant API
    participant Parser as Dedicated JSON Level Parser
    participant Meta
    participant Time
    participant Env
    participant Handoff

    Config->>Config: Resolve JSON schema + level parser
    API->>Parser: JSON text content only
    Parser-->>Env: Parsed JSON field view
    Meta-->>Env: Prepared metadata
    Time-->>Env: Stabilized timestamp
    Env->>Handoff: Envelope exposure contract
